reviews.text: Soup is nice here, but the chicken is just ok

This is a restaurant that sells high quality Hainan chicken and related dishes.  Love the chickens.  Will visit next time too.

result.name: Golden Chicken

reviews.text: Small restaurant with big reputation. Tried the chicken and the pig's knuckle, their pieces de resistance. Both done to perfection. Price was very user-friendly too. Place is usually jam-packed during meal hours, so go at off-peak times or be prepared to wait and have your meal rubbing shoulders with everyone else.

Tasty meal but the restaurant is small and you won’t have adequate and relaxing time/atmosphere to enjoy the food.Typical HK style restaurant .One lunch set served with pumpkin soup only costs you $52. Reasonable price.
Specialised at Hai Nam Chicken rice which is ok at hkd50+.  The portion is relatively small if u hv a big stomach.
The best Hainanese Chicken rice. Much better than their branch in Tsuen Wan
Good taste. The must go restaurant in Sai Kung

result.name: 金雞去骨海南雞專門店

reviews.text: 好好食👍一定要試!
海南雞飯好吃 豬腳也好吃 但味道太重 人多再點豬腳比較合適
還可以吧！菜色小了點。
雞滑，油飯0K。店舖太小，有擠迫感覺。進食時不時有外賣，人多出入。
經過多次比較，只有在西貢店，有點隱蔽的小巷，才吃到最有雞味的黃油海南雞，勝過很多餐廳的出品！雞油飯也不俗，加了乾蔥，更勝一籌！質素出眾價錢親民。

a very convenience shopping mall with all needs for daily life, various kind of restaurant s, supermarket and grocery shops.
